==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Carbonite
<hw>Car"bon*ite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Carbon</ets>
+ <ets>-ite</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An explosive consisting
essentially of nitroglycerin, wood meal, and some nitrate, as that of
sodium.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An explosive composed of nitrobenzene, saltpeter,
sulphur, and kieselguhr.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Carbonization</ent>⟦br⟧
